      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "BOISE, Jan. Alleging that he\nwas libeled In an interview from\nGov. Frank Gooding in the Boise\nStatesman, in which Gooding re-\npiled to articles signed by State\nAuditor Bragaw in regard TO con-\ntroversy over the fund used to pay\nexpenses of the Pettibone and\nHaywood trials, Bragaw today\nbrought suit against Gooding and\nthe Statesman for $4,000.\n\n\nBragaw's articles appeared In the\nCapital News."
